data.description: Balmoral offers residents connected living with luxurious homes built by exceptional builders that are set within charming gated, non-gated and lakeside villages. When it's time to play, residents have many amenities to choose from, including the Houston area's Crystal Clear Lagoon surrounded by glistening white sand beaches.Balmoral's prime location allows residents to easily access major employers such as downtown Houston, the major industrial and petrochemical employers in east Houston, the Texas Medical Center and the dynamic Generation Park, a 4,000-acre mixed-use mega development.
